## Verified gotchas
- **Pre-audit, EVERY upload is locked to `private`** — not unlisted, not
  public. Both raw-VOD-unlisted and Shorts-public visibility wait on the
  audit. We can build/test fully with private uploads; audit flips visibility
  later. (Confirmed vs Google docs, Jul 2026.)
- Upload = **1,600 quota units** each; default 10k/day ≈ **6 uploads/day**.
- OAuth "Testing" mode refresh tokens can expire in ~7 days; a long-lived
  token needs the consent screen published ("In production"). Resolve when
  wiring `youtube-login.js`.

